column1: IF ccr_thf_d is MF 1 AND ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_sa_dihydrotest_d is MF 1 AND ccr_thb_d is MF 1 AND ccr_s_at_d is MF 2 AND ccr_a_cortol_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_cortisone_d is MF 2 AND ccr_llb_oh_andro_d is MF 2 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 1
IF ccr_sb_oh_f_d is MF 0 AND ccr_thaldo_d is MF 0 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 2 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 1  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 0
